{
  "stem": "10818.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As it turned out, it was difficult still to get an affidavit of support, because of the depression here in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the whole idea was if we have to go someplace, we'll go to America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the question, the well-known question of getting a visa number came up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father, I guess-- oh, you know, one of the times he was in Frankfurt, l he got a visa number.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was for 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On the Kristallnacht, which I guess you're going to come to, he went to Frankfurt again and got one for his parents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was for a year later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, that was already too late.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the reason-- one reason that we didn't immigrate earlier is A, the business has been quite good up to that point.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "B, the parents were-- my mother's parents had died by 1933.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My father's parents were elderly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We would have-- they would have had to be supported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would've-- it would've been very difficult for them to move.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then the other thing is-- well, for one thing, we felt it would blow over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you don't leave the country of your birth lightly, even if it had been easy to make another career.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You live where you live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You have-- you have your roots there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Literally roots.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, some of the books that I have just been going through express it extremely well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, this-- you've lived there-- your family's lived there for hundreds and hundreds of years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You have no reason to think that because some house painter from Austria is coming along that you have to leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so [LAUGHS] you wait until it's almost too late.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And a lot of people waited until it was too late.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
